        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q"><span data-lang="en">What's different from upstream Warp?</span><span data-lang="zh">和上游 Warp 有什么差别?</span><span class="plus">+</span></summary>
          <div class="faq-a" data-lang="en">Six things: AI provider (any vs cloud gateway), credentials (local vs cloud account), prompts (minijinja editable vs server-assembled), third-party CLI agents (DeepSeek-TUI / Codex / Claude Code wired in vs none), SSH + tmux (built-in vs none), cloud features (off vs on by default). Plus rendering fixes for code blocks, tables and CJK soft-wrap. Everything else from upstream stays.</div>
